saadadb.meta
Interface DMInterface

All Known Implementing Classes:
ClassDMTester, ClassDMTester._ssa_default, CubeSaada, EntrySaada, FlatfileSaada, ImageSaada, MiscSaada, Position, SaadaInstance, SpectrumSaada, TableSaada, WCSSaada
public interface DMInterface

This interface is used by Saada instance to implement datamodels. Classes implementing DMInterface are always inner classes of @SaadaInstance A SaadaInstance contains one DMInterface implementation for each implemented datamodel. Methods of the interface are used as accessors by the SaadaInstance

Author:
michel
